g alt=\u0022KSP2-SPECS-v7-FINAL-Poppe_Version-3-plsl\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022164.00\u0022 height=\u0022674\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1039965330774175784/1076223449971818556/KSP2-SPECS-v7-FINAL-Poppe_Version-3-plsletthisbefinal-2.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis just feels fake. But I hope it\u0027s not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-17T19:38:36Z\u0022 title=\u002202/17/2023 07:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 17, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Vl3d\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LHACK4142","CreatedById":208897,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:37:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224233665\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221676662621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis just feels fake.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOfficial Intercept discord...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bombaatu","CreatedById":157643,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:38:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224233665\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221676662621\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis just feels fake.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope. Posted by PD | Dakota on the Kerbal 2 discord #faqs channel. It\u0027s official.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zeekzeek22","CreatedById":223169,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:39:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, still going to boot it up on my 5-year-old laptop, probably with graphics cranked as low as they\u2019ll go. No regerts. Also, remember, we all have until full release to build a new pc. Also whatever those streamed-gaming services might work?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:39:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s awesome! Very glad to hear we\u0027re getting a modern game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LHACK4142","CreatedById":208897,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:40:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe discord is beautiful right now\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SolarAdmiral","CreatedById":107350,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:41:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224233662\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221676662470\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222736\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mcpattyp\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, mcpattyp said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDamn my 2070 is just barely above the minimum\u2026 wait\u2026 3080 \u00A0RECOMMENDED???!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI asked this in the other post for the system specs. But I was wondering what resolutions they\u0027re talking about. Anyone know how other games do it nowadays?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike is it maybe RTX 3080 recommended for 4k and minimum 2060 for 1080p?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stephensan","CreatedById":222320,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-17T19:41:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224233675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221676662866\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022107350\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SolarAdmiral\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, SolarAdmiral said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI asked this in the other post for the system specs. But I was wondering what resolutions they\u0027re talking about. Anyone know how other games do it nowadays?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike is it maybe RTX 3080 recommended for 4k and minimum 2060 for 1080p?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nto think that you need a 2060 for 1080p.. it should be 1440p@60fps med high... like\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}